subject: from Barrister Jeremiah Bonigas
body:
Hello Dear Myung

Thanks for your reply, I am sorry for getting back to you late. I had a couple of court cases which I just concluded. I intentionally contacted you so the bank can transfer the fund to you for out both mutual benefit instead of losing the fund to the bank, which by the end of the day will be shared among some top corrupt bank officials. Please give me your whatsapp number so I can give you details on how we can achieve this smoothly.

Thanks and I wait.

Jeremiah Bonigas, Esq.
